description:
In celebration of the summer's most eagerly anticipated film, MAN OF STEEL: ALL-STAR SUPERMAN #1 by Grant Morrison and Frank Quietly is the first chapter in the best-selling series ALL-STAR SUPERMAN.

The cover is a reprint of the complete trade paperback edition of the series, originally released in 2011.

name: Transformation and Triumph

volume.name: Knights of the Dinner Table: Illustrated

description: Join the misadventures of Knuckles, El Ravager, Zayre and Teflon Billy as they wreak havoc with their unique brand of heroics. This issue re-tells the KoDT strips Five Green Towels, A Call for Heroes, Coward of the County, and Balance of Terror, from the perspective of their HackMaster role-playing game characters. This issue also includes the original Balance of Terror as a backup KoDT strip!
